        "TileImage": "$($repository a66d5c7c-79cb-4472-9e66-4008c51f6f02).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47. Your primary target is Signore Ettore de Marco from Sapienza. He has been working with three other local bodyguards to recieve shipments of handguns from French Policemen. I ask that you kill two of the bodyguards in anyway you want, but that you kill the middle one with a screwdie to the face. Got it? Good luck.\r\r\rOriginal Epic Contract by Eclipse :)",
